(16 Oct 2017)  To compile with openMP on fock, with ifort

source /opt/intel/bin/compilervars.sh intel64

(17 oct 2017)  May need to set number of OpenMP threads, e.g., 
setenv OMP_NUM_THREADS 6

REMEMBER:  
export NCIPLOT_HOME=~/nciplot-data/


Added a new keyword "SHORT" that suppresses all the long outputs and doesn't allocate big arrays, write dat or cube files, etc.

